import React, { useState } from "react"; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import "./UserProfile.css"; export default function UserProfile() { const navigate = useNavigate(); const user = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("user")); if (!user) { return (
User not logged in.
); } const handleLogout = () => { localStorage.removeItem("user"); navigate("/login"); }; // Track which sections are open const [open, setOpen] = useState({ personal: true, address: false, health: false, prefs: false, security: false, }); const toggleSection = (key) => setOpen((prev) => ({ ...prev, [key]: !prev[key] })); return (

👤 My Profile

{/* Personal Info */}

toggleSection("personal")} > Personal Information

{open.personal && (
Name {user.name}
Email {user.email}
Phone {user.phone || "—"}
Date of Birth {user.dob || "—"}
Gender {user.gender || "—"}
)}
{/* Address */}

toggleSection("address")} > Address

{open.address && (
Street {user.address?.street || "—"}
City {user.address?.city || "—"}
State {user.address?.state || "—"}
Pincode {user.address?.pincode || "—"}
)}
{/* Health Details */}

toggleSection("health")} > Health Information

{open.health && (
Allergies {user.allergies || "—"}
Current Medications {user.currentMedications || "—"}
Chronic Conditions {user.chronicConditions || "—"}
)}
{/* Preferences */}

toggleSection("prefs")} > Preferences

{open.prefs && (
Communication {user.communicationPref || "—"}
Refill Reminders {user.refillReminders ? "Enabled" : "Disabled"}
)}
{/* Security */}

toggleSection("security")} > Account Security

{open.security && (
Role {user.role}
Two-Factor Auth {user.twoFactor ? "Enabled" : "Disabled"}
)}
); }
